# Context Lifecycle Concern Atom
concern: context-lifecycle
triggers: ["15+ exchanges", "compress context", "token warning"]
load_when: session exceeds 15 exchanges or token threshold reached

## Compression Trigger Conditions
|Condition|Threshold|Action|
|------|------|------|
|Exchange count|Current session 20+ exchanges|Recommend compression|
|Code block accumulation|5+ large code blocks|Recommend compression|
|Token estimate warning|warning_threshold reached|Immediate compression recommendation|
|Response quality degradation|Repeating previous content, confusion signals|Immediate compression recommendation|
|User explicit request|`compress context`|Execute immediately|
|New session start|SUMMARY.md exists|Auto-load|

Agent: when compression conditions detected, finish current work then recommend compression. For token emergency (critical), start compression immediately after response.

## SUMMARY.md Format
```markdown
# Context Summary
<!-- auto-generated by Agent — do not edit manually -->
<!-- source_sessions: [session_YYYYMMDD_001, ...] -->
<!-- created: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ -->
<!-- updated: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ -->
## Project State
- Current phase: (e.g. Bootstrap 5 migration 60% complete)
- Last completed: (e.g. Header, Footer converted)
- Next task: (e.g. Card component conversion)
## Key Decisions Made
- [YYYY-MM-DD] (decision) — (reason) — details: DECISIONS.md
## Resolved Issues
- (resolved problem summary — for prevention)
## Active Constraints
- (constraints that MUST be honored now)
## Open Questions
- (unresolved items)
## Session Thread (last 5 exchanges)
1. [User] (summary)
2. [Agent] (summary)
3. [User] (summary)
4. [Agent] (summary)
5. [User] (summary) → current position
```

## INDEX.md Format
```markdown
# Archive Index
## Session Directory
|File|Date|Exchanges|Key Topics|
|------|------|------|------|
|session_YYYYMMDD_001.md|YYYY-MM-DD|N exchanges|(keywords)|
## Topic Index
|Topic|File|Exchange #|
|------|------|------|
|(topic)|session_YYYYMMDD_001.md|#N~#M|
## Code Artifact Index
|Artifact|File|Exchange #|
|------|------|------|
|(code description)|session_YYYYMMDD_001.md|#N|
```

## Compression Execution
```
1. Save current session dialogue as archive file
   → .ai.dev/context/archive/session_YYYYMMDD_NNN.md
2. Load existing SUMMARY.md (if any)
3. Merge new dialogue into summary:
   - Update Project State
   - Add Key Decisions
   - Add Resolved Issues
   - Refresh Open Questions
   - Session Thread: keep only last 5 exchanges
4. Update INDEX.md:
   - Add new file to Session Directory
   - Add topics to Topic Index
   - Add code to Code Artifact Index
5. Report completion:
   "[Compression Complete]
    Archive: session_YYYYMMDD_NNN.md (N exchanges)
    SUMMARY.md will auto-load next session."
```

## Session Restart Auto-Load
```
New session start:
1. Check .ai.dev/context/SUMMARY.md
   → Missing: normal start
   → Exists: auto-load and output:
"[Previous Context Restored]
 Project: {Project State}
 Last task: {last completed}
 Next: {next task}
 Open questions: {N} items
 Continue?"
```

## Archive Search
압축된 요약만으로 답하기 어려울 때:
```
Triggers:
  - Past decision/code reference requests
  - SUMMARY.md info insufficient
  - Detailed code artifacts needed

Procedure:
1. Scan INDEX.md Topic Index or Code Artifact Index
   → find relevant session file and exchange numbers
2. Read only the relevant exchange sections from archive
   → NEVER read entire archive file (token saving)
3. Inject found content into current context
   → "[Archive Search] session_YYYYMMDD_001.md #exchange{N}"
4. If not found:
   → scan most relevant session file
   → still not found: ask user directly
```

## Commands
|Command|Action|
|------|------|
|`compress context`|Immediate session compression, archive, index update|
|`show context summary`|Display SUMMARY.md content|
|`search archive: <keyword>`|Search INDEX.md, return relevant archive sections|
|`show context index`|Display full INDEX.md|
|`reset context`|Initialize SUMMARY.md (preserve archives)|
